Description:
    Stubs out a model and a view for a new cluster 
    task. Pass the task name as the first argument.

Usage:
     script/generate cluster_task TaskName [--advanced]

Options:
     --advanced : will include templates for the advanced
                  CbrainTask::Portal API methods in the
                  Ruby code template for the task.

Example:

     script/generate cluster_task UniversalTranslator

will create these templates:

     app/models/cbrain_task/universal_translator.rb
     app/views/tasks/cbrain_task/_universal_translator.html.erb

